flowchart TD
    A[User request] --> B{Context needed?}
    B -->|Yes| C[Hook injects info]
    B -->|No| D[Proceed directly]
    C --> E{Search needed?}
    D --> E
    E -->|Yes| F[MCP searches fragments]
    E -->|No| G[Generate response]
    F --> G
    G --> H{Complex task?}
